{"tid":150166,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【中環人語●生成鬼仔樣】父母都係中國人 此子何來問句妻","createTime":"2017-03-09T22:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T21:23:01.000Z","uid":51978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"891df87e66bb76334db9c8d04ddbe0fe286e680a","tid":150166,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T22:17:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/recommend/20170310/485615\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Frecommend%2F20170310%2F485615&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOoM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=7849300f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Frecommend%2F20170310%2F485615&h=15db7e0d\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/recommend/20170310/485615</a><br />\n（有片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上市半日就被證監勒令停牌的駿傑（8188），焦點遂落在其保薦人浩德融資老細，即葉劉姪仔葉天賜（Arnold）身上，其父為正興建築創辦人葉正平長子，母親為前軍閥陳維周孫女陳潔麗，貴為名門之後，且畢業於英國劍橋名校，外形討好，是正牌「金融才俊」，但中環口痕友提出一個非常奧妙問題，何解Arnold相貌好像混血兒，其父葉文山及母親陳潔麗都係中國人面孔，莫非父母有隱性洋人基因？套用死鬼曹仁超一句，木宰羊？只可以講一句，貴為葉家的長孫，葉天賜沒分得家族分毫，全靠自己一雙手，或者重溫任劍輝主演的《此子何來問句妻》或者有些頭緒。"},{"pid":"fd1332231def2eb96a5f7bee67743f2cd26326fc","tid":150166,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T22:18:13.000Z","msg":"有冇清知啲料？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd6e08025a6c1b0573679857a95588aab97735ab","tid":150166,"uid":74442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T22:30:16.000Z","msg":"洋腸換太子"},{"pid":"ef39229997b2b8810bb653dd0efec9988acc5b36","tid":150166,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T22:50:20.000Z","msg":"是咪有料爆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0d3e9bfb26980f5fb1493947710f3ae68a3111","tid":150166,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T22:50: